          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632736750762-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chilli is cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>– this is your <strong>herby</strong> <strong>rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632736755025-x200.jpg",
